codex
I found a concrete bug in the verifier’s path search: it estimates eMode borrow capacity using `flashAmount = 1` for every route, then compares real repayment needs against that tiny stale estimate. That can make every otherwise-valid route look unprofitable and explains the zero-profit outcome in the logs. I’m patching the search so the debt-opening amount is sized against the actual collateral being flash-funded.
